title: Thai Erawan Thai Cuisine
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Ovo, Thai, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. In a town with no pure vegetarian eateries, you can sometimes try a Thai food restaurant and get a vegetable dish, like a vegetable stir fry. Specify that you are vegan/vegetarian and tell them to omit fish sauce and shrimp paste. Ask for tofu as the protein option. Here, the menu includes sections labeled as "vegetarian corner." Contemporary Thai-themed decor with buddhas and warm gold colors.
